{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9ff2a66687","title":"和李宗仁及其夫人的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"19d187fc77","index":0,"year":1965,"month":7,"day":27,"articleId":"9ff2a66687"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/48-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji48":{"comments":[{"id":"18b2ce57d0","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"9ff2a66687","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李宗仁，原为国民党桂系首领。1948年4月任国民党政府副总统，1949年1月蒋介石引退后任国民党政府代总统。国民党政权崩溃后去美国。他借夫人郭德洁1965年7月从海外归来，20日到达北京。"}],"contents":[{"id":"d264283680","type":"title","text":"和李宗仁\"及其夫人的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"9ff2a66687"},{"id":"18b2ce57d0","type":"paragraph","text":"【新华社二十七日讯】毛泽东主席今天中午接见季宗仁先生和他的夫人郭德洁女士。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"9ff2a66687"},{"id":"ea32ccbec6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席同李宗仁先生及其天人热烈握手。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"9ff2a66687"},{"id":"d9bbbb6249","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席说：你们回来，很好，欢迎你们。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"9ff2a66687"},{"id":"fdea7ef57a","type":"paragraph","text":"李宗仁先生说：我们回来后都为祖国的强大感到高兴","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"9ff2a66687"},{"id":"a72d6674d5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席说：祖国是比过去强大了一些，但还不很强大，我们至少还得再建设二三十年才能真正强大起来。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"9ff2a66687"},{"id":"d9e5c174a4","type":"paragraph","text":"李宗仁先生对毛主席说，在海外的许多人士都怀念祖国，他们渴望回到祖国来。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"9ff2a66687"},{"id":"dca89d490e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席说：跑到海外的，凡是愿意回来，我们都欢迎。他们回来，我们都以礼相待。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"9ff2a66687"},{"id":"4cc33a0d1e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席建议李宗仁先生到全国各地去看看","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"9ff2a66687"}],"page":{"id":"39e4795f2f","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"9ff2a66687","start":127,"end":127}}}},"__N_SSG":true}